mas.agentsHempelsSofa.data

Class AgentToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • mas.agentsHempelsSofa.data.AgentToken
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<AgentToken>, Believable

    public class AgentToken
extends Object
implements Believable, Comparable<AgentToken>
    An implementation of an agent token which includes the following information about an agent:
    • the name
    • the team
    • the position
    • the role
    • the strategy
    • the energy
    • the maximum energy
    • the maximum energy if disabled
    • the health
    • the maximum health
    • the strength
    • the visibility range
    • the target vertex
    • the target agent
    • the step it was lastly inspected
    It can be placed and moved on the Graph.
    Author:
    Hempels-Sofa
